Sky: <i>I need to talk to Dad first!</i>
===

title: Cumulus
position: -117,10
---
<<if $motherFinished == false>>
<<once>>
<<toggleExclamation Cumulus>>

Cumulus: “What’s up, kiddo? You’re up early.” #line:0cb9aac 

//(Cumulus looks up at Sky, properly noting her expression)

Cumulus: “Hmmm, you look like you got thunderclouds crashing in your head.” #line:0dfda14 

Sky: “...Dad I think I heard something… A voice, and it called for me!” #line:07ad266 

Cumulus: “The wind carries many voices across Ethor. Most people have stopped listening” #line:012beff 

Sky: “Dad! Listen to me! Something about it felt so… real” #line:05cc2b8 

Cumulus: “Real, you say? What did you hear, then?” #line:08b8f3f 

Sky: “It said the islands are in danger, and something about a hero, and -” #line:0b2b470 

Cumulus: “A hero… so the Mother Crystal truly has called for you…” #line:0d91667 

Sky: “What? How do you know, dad?” #line:016c213 

Cumulus: “When you were younger you also mentioned that voice. I thought that, over time, maybe you had forgotten…” #line:09c0cf7 

Cumulus: “But the fact of the matter is that you’ve always had the strongest connection to the crystal more than the rest of us on the island. #line:0d161b8 

Cumulus: And if you feel called… you should go see her.” #line:0757bfa 

//(Camera briefly pans to Mother Crystal’s Temple)

<<disableInvisWall CumulusWall>>
<<enableInvisWall CrystalCallWall>>
<<endonce>>

<b>Go to Mother Crystal</b> #line:0a2c696 

<<else>>
<<once>>
<<toggleExclamation Cumulus>>
Cumulus: Back so soon, kiddo? You look like you’ve seen a hurricane.

Sky: Dad! You were right! Mother Crystal really did call me! She gave me her blessing!

Cumulus: So it’s time… 

Cumulus: That aura… it carries the Mother Crystal’s power, correct?

Sky: Yep! But I need a way to travel to the other islands. Mother Crystal says her powers are useless to me if I can’t travel across Ethor!

Cumulus: Aha! You don’t even have to ask! After all, it’s my duty as your father to provide for you.

Sky: Aww Dad!...

Cumulus: Climb aboard, Sky! You’ll reach the closest island if you follow the wind!

Cumulus: I hear this island is quite chilly. You’ll know you’re close when you begin to pass through the relentless frigid winds.

Sky: Got it! Thanks, Dad!

Sky: <i>Well…here goes nothing! I’ve got to save Ethor!</i>

<<disableInvisWall AirshipColliderWall>>
<<enableInvisWall AirshipDialogueWall>>

<<endonce>>

Cumulus: Go on kiddo, the ship’s all yours now!

<<endif>>
